title: Use 2FA From Your Tui
tags: @zettel _method ctop
roam-id: c4a31024-5d77-4df0-916a-d3eec7249f11
type: text/markdown

- install `ctop` from nixpkgs
- the following example will create a new OTP labeled as google

``` shell
ctop add -l google
```

- it will ask you the password for cotp
- enter the secret
- run `ctop` again
- enter the password
- you'll see your otp
